Prompt for Website-Creation-AI

Create a fully responsive, modern, and fluid website for the professional brand Jason Shadow. The site represents a multidisciplinary performer specializing in:

Singing / Vocal Performance

Voice Acting / Synchronisation

Moderation / Hosting

Brand & Visual Direction

Aesthetic: Modern, cinematic, and immersive.

Style Keywords: fiery accents, shadow-themed depth, dark-mode base, glowing highlights, sleek gradients, professional stage-like atmosphere.

Color Palette: Deep blacks/charcoal greys, subtle ember-reds, warm orange glows, metallic silver tones for contrast.

Typography: Clean, bold, high-legibility fonts suitable for media/entertainment brands.

Visual Identity: Integrate fire-like reflections, soft shadow layers, and motion effects that communicate dynamism and vocal intensity. Avoid clutter; prioritize a flexible and scalable layout.

Core Requirements

Hero Section

Full-width cinematic header.

Strong headline introducing “Jason Shadow – Voice, Performance, Presence.”

Background animation or parallax blending shadows and ember-light.

Service Sections

Dedicated subsections for Singing, Voice-Acting, and Moderation.

Each with clear value propositions, differentiation points, and booking options.

Audio & Video Integration

Embedded audio reels, showreels, voice-acting demos, or performance clips.

Player must be fully responsive and lightweight.

Portfolio / Showcase

Grid or carousel displaying past performances, studio recordings, moderation events, collaborations, and notable productions.

Space for client logos if needed.

About Section

Professional biography with focus on artistic identity, vocal range, experience, and brand positioning.

Contact & Booking

Clean, optimized form with fields for project type, budget range, and required deliverables.

Include direct links for business email or social media channels.

UX & Technical Requirements

Fully responsive across all devices.

Smooth transitions and micro-interactions.

Fast loading, accessibility-compliant, and SEO-optimized.

Modular content blocks for easy future expansion.

Tone & Positioning

Present the brand as a high-end, reliable, and versatile creative professional. Emphasize performance expertise, vocal mastery, and consistent delivery quality.
